   ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   This repository contains Junction — the production ECL harness for the
   Eidolons project. Junction is the first-party runtime that dispatches
   Eidolons over their installed `commands/*.sh` entry points and treats
   every hand-off as an ECL v1.0 envelope on disk.

   Junction composes with — but is independent of — Rynaro/eidolons-ecl
   (the wire-format spec) and Rynaro/eidolons-eiis (the install standard).
   Each Eidolon repository may use its own license; Junction itself is
   Apache-2.0.

   For the full Apache-2.0 text, see:
   https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt
